@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Seeded rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms

### Availability (replace dates as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/availability?check_in=2030-06-10&check_out=2030-06-12

### Reserve an available room
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guest_name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "guest_email": "ada@example.com",
  "room_id": 101,
  "check_in": "2030-06-10",
  "check_out": "2030-06-12"
}

### Get reservation (replace 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/1

### Cancel a future reservation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reservations/1

### Check in (reservation must begin today)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/1/check-in

### Check out
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/1/check-out

### Housekeeping marks the room ready after checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/101/ready
